divs: Sighting DetailsI was on north hwy 465 before exit 65 i was driving.I thought it was a light off of another car but it was not. saw one round ball like object in the air.It was a dull white light.Saw just one at first then saw about 12 all stuck togather. i have never saw anything like this before.
Summary: Round ball like objects over road.
